<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8406656>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Photos of details of leaves showing the characteristic thickened pale olivaceous margins of Calea (Neurolaeneae,Asteraceae) species belonging to the Monocephala clade. A. Abaxial side of C. ilienii leaf; B. Abaxial side of foliaceous phyllaries from C. ilienii; C. Leaf margins leaf of C. monocephala. A, B (G. Johsson 141a, K); C (P. K. H. Dusén 7599, K)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8406656/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8406658>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Comparison of informative structures to recognize the new nothospecies Calea × crassa (first column) in relation to its parental species C. ilienii (second column) and C. monocephala (third column) (Neurolaeneae, Asteraceae). A–C. Shape of first series of phyllaries and indumentum of the abaxial side. D–I. Ray florets and disc florets. J–L. Indumentum of abaxial surface of ray florets corollas. M–R. Cypselae and pappus scales.A, D, E, J, M and N: Calea monocephala drawn from G. Hatschbach et al. 35885 (MBM). B, F, G, K, O and P: Calea × crassa drawn from J.M. Silva et al. 8265 (MBM). C, H, I, L, Q and R: Calea ilienii drawn from T.F. Santos 347 (ICN). A–R: millimeter scale. Illustration by Débora Dalzotto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8406658/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8406660>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Occurrence map of Calea × crassa, C. ilienii, and C. monocephala (Neurolaeneae, Asteraceae) in Brazil. PR: Paraná State, SC: Santa Catarina State." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8406660/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8406662>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Prediction occurrence map of suitable ecological niche modelling for Calea ilienii and C. monocephala (Neurolaeneae, Asteraceae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8406662/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8406664>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Prediction occurrence map of suitable ecological niche modelling for Calea × crassa based on overlapping occurrence areas of C. ilienii and C. monocephala (Neurolaeneae, Asteraceae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8406664/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

